        <section class="text-center mb-16 pt-8">
            <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Slips, Trips, and Falls</h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">An interactive guide to understanding and preventing common workplace accidents. Your safety is paramount.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="risks" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Understand the Risks</h3>
                <p class="text-md text-gray-500 mt-2">Knowing the difference is the first step to prevention.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-4">Slip</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Occurs with too little friction between footwear and the walking surface, leading to a loss of balance.</p>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold mb-2">Common Causes:</h5>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600">
                        <li>Spills, puddles, or ice</li>
                        <li>Wet or oily surfaces</li>
                        <li>Loose rugs or mats</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-4">Trip</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Occurs when the foot hits an object, and the upper body continues moving, causing a loss of balance.</p>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold mb-2">Common Causes:</h5>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600">
                        <li>Clutter (cords, boxes)</li>
                        <li>Poor lighting</li>
                        <li>Uneven surfaces (steps, carpets)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                    <h4 class="text-2xl font-bold text-red-600 mb-4">Fall</h4>
                    <p class="mb-4 text-gray-600">Occurs when you are too far off your center of balance to recover, resulting from a slip or trip.</p>
                    <h5 class="font-semibold mb-2">Types of Falls:</h5>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-gray-600">
                        <li><span class="font-medium">At same level:</span> Onto the walking surface.</li>
                        <li><span class="font-medium">To lower level:</span> From a height or into an object.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="prevention" class="mb-16 scroll-mt-20">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Prevention Checklists</h3>
                <p class="text-md text-gray-500 mt-2">Use these actionable tips to create a safer environment.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center mb-8">
                <div class="bg-gray-200 rounded-lg p-1 flex space-x-1">
                    <button id="slip-btn" class="tab-button py-2 px-6 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors duration-300 active">Prevent Slips</button>
                    <button id="trip-btn" class="tab-button py-2 px-6 rounded-md font-medium transition-colors duration-300">Prevent Trips</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="slip-content" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Wipe shoes thoroughly on mats when entering.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Wipe up any spills immediately, even small ones.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Mark slippery areas with a sign until they are clean and dry.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-blue-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>If you see a hazard on the floor, clean it up if you can.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="trip-content" class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg hidden">
                 <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 gap-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Walk slowly and pay attention to your surroundings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Ensure your path is well-lit; replace burnt-out bulbs.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Keep walkways clear of clutter like boxes, bags, and cords.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Close drawers and cabinet doors immediately after use.</p>
                    </div>
                     <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Report or correct hazards like curled rugs or chipped flooring.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start space-x-3">
                        <span class="text-amber-500 font-bold text-xl mt-1">✓</span>
                        <p>Carry only loads you can see over to maintain a clear line of sight.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="stats" class="mb-8 scroll-mt-20">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800">Key Statistics</h3>
                <p class="text-md text-gray-500 mt-2">Understanding the data behind falls.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">The majority of falls are the result of slips and trips on the same level. Falls from a height, while often more severe, are less common. This highlights the critical importance of good housekeeping and situational awareness in preventing most fall-related incidents.</p>
                <div class="chart-container">
